{"tid":298318,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《神奇女俠》Gal Gadot片酬僅234萬港幣","createTime":"2017-06-26T07:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T10:34:22.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b5b3912b8d800df49cfb893466dead5c0531676","tid":298318,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:57:53.000Z","msg":"Gal Gadot 所飾演女主角的超級英雄電影《Wonder Woman》大獲好評，全球票房已超過 5.7 億美元，但原來她的片酬並沒有想像中的高。據《The Daily Dot》報導，Gal Gadot 以每部收 30 萬美元的片酬，與 DC&nbsp;簽定了 3 部片約，而伴隨已完成的《Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice》、《Wonder Woman》，以及快將上映的《Justice League》，Gal Gadot 的片約亦將要重新簽定，在利好消息的影響下，相信她將可獲得更高的片酬。然而，這不是第一位荷李活巨星收到如此低的片酬，據報導指出 Captain America 扮演者 Chris Evans 的片酬亦只是 30 萬美元。當然，Gal Gadot 將有機會從《Wonder Woman》票房中獲得分紅，據悉擔任 Iron Man 的 Robert Downey Jr. 就曾獲得 5,000 萬美元，而飾演超人的 Henry Cavill 亦從超人電影《Man of Steel》中收到 1,400 萬美元分紅，算是對於片酬低的極大安慰！"},{"pid":"52d6e2b509174354c984f6ccfb4cab26cfa93640","tid":298318,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T08:08:17.000Z","msg":"分紅先係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b157baa06857ce44cca05f2ce509a6eee1ec7a1","tid":298318,"uid":45821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T08:10:44.000Z","msg":"啲廣告排住隊搵佢拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5370a65c637e3e41ad00f03f434be66365059a09","tid":298318,"uid":9105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T08:29:35.000Z","msg":"依家紅左之後大把世界啦<br />\n加上佢本身都極有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ceb86d47fdfbd63e97010852990f51711d29ed5","tid":298318,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T09:06:45.000Z","msg":"使唔使呀<br />\n<br />\n幾日一個post話佢片酬低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9774e8bff2ecac906aafba980b1a5d81608c10c7","tid":2983